// Theme button html
---

<button id="theme_button" class="flex dark:bg-indigo-500 bg-indigo-400">
  <span
    id="light_theme"
    title="Light theme"
    class="text-xl hover:cursor-pointer px-2 pt-1 border-2 border-black dark:border-indigo-500"
    >🐓</span
  >
  <span
    id="dark_theme"
    title="Dark theme"
    class="text-xl hover:cursor-pointer px-2 pt-1 border-2 dark:border-white border-indigo-400"
    >🦉</span
  >
</button>
